<h1 id="statistical-insight-widgets">Statistical Insight Widgets</h1>

<p>Watford Insights Requests:</p>
<blockquote>
  <p>Having additional widgets to provide statistical insights will be beneficial, but also optional per user.</p>

  <p>Having specific league tables and cumulative charts to highlight statistical trends and insights such as:</p>

  <ul>
    <li>Weekly Positional Statistical Rankings (easily manipulated per league, age, position etc)</li>
    <li>Cumulative table of all players in the system that have been reported on</li>
    <li>Shortlist/Table of players based on Position Specific data (to be discussed)</li>
  </ul>
</blockquote>

